### TC-001 | Airtel Airtime VTU — ₦100 to 08011111111 (expect: delivered)
POST {{base}}/pay
api-key: {{apiKey}}
secret-key: {{secret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "request_id": "{{date}}-TC001",
  "serviceID": "airtel",
  "amount": 100,
  "phone": "{{phone}}"
}

