secret-key: {{secret}}

###

### TC-036b | Home Cover Insurance — purchase
### Verify exact serviceID and variation_code from TC-036a
POST {{base}}/pay
api-key: {{apiKey}}
secret-key: {{secret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "request_id": "{{date}}-TC036",
  "serviceID": "home-cover-insurance",
  "variation_code": "home-cover",
  "billersCode": "{{phone}}",
  "amount": 5000,
  "phone": "{{phone}}"
}

