# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  REQUERY — poll any pending/timed-out transaction
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### REQUERY | Poll transaction status by request_id
### Replace request_id with the ID of the transaction to check
POST {{base}}/requery
api-key: {{apiKey}}
secret-key: {{secret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "request_id": "{{date}}-TC001"
}

